About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2" is the sixth film of the YRF Spy Universe franchise and will release on 14 August 2025. The film stars two of the greatest cinematic icons Hrithik Roshan and NTR, with Kiara Advani in the lead and is directed by Ayan Mukerji. ‚ÄúAlpha‚Äù, the seventh instalment in the franchise and Hindi cinema's first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, is set to release on 25 December 2025.

snippet.title: [EN] 2025 PMWC at EWC Survival Stage D1 | PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP
snippet.description:
SURVIVAL STAGE DAY 1 | JULY 29

The 2025 PUBG MOBILE WORLD CUP at ESPORTS WORLD CUP enters a critical phase as the Survival Stage kicks off in Riyadh! The battle intensifies as teams fight for their last chance to reach the Grand Finals and claim their share of the massive $3,000,000 prize pool.

This stage is do-or-die. After the Group Stage, the top 8 teams already secured their Grand Finals slots‚Äîbut for the remaining 16 teams, the Survival Stage is their only shot. Over the course of two days, these teams will clash head-to-head, with only 8 advancing to Grand Finals. The pressure is immense. The stakes? Everything.

The Survival Stage is where stories are rewritten and underdogs rise. With limited spots left, every match, every zone, and every elimination could decide a team‚Äôs fate. Which 8 will survive and BEAT THE HEAT?

üî• Why You Can‚Äôt Miss 2025 PMWC at EWC:
- High-pressure matches for survival!
- 16 teams, only 8 tickets to the Grand Finals!
- Cheer for your favorite region and team as they chase the $3,000,000 and a crown!
- Exciting SMASH RULE format in Grand Finals! 

üî• How does SMASH RULE work in Grand Finals? 
After Day 2 of Grand Finals, the Match Point Threshold will be set to the #1 ranked team‚Äôs points +10. Any team that hits this must then win a later match to claim the trophy in the last day of Grand Finals‚Äîwinning the same match where they reach the threshold doesn‚Äôt bring the championship. If no team secures the title via SMASH Rule by Match 18, the team with the highest total points wins under standard rules.

snippet.title: Main Kisi Aur Ka Hun Filhal | Akshay Kumar Ft Nupur Sanon | B Praak, Jaani | Arvindr K | Ammy Virk
snippet.description:
#jaani  #filhall #akshaykumar #bpraak  
Have you ever selflessly loved someone so much that just their smile can brighten up your day? 

FILHALL, a feel good song about love and it‚Äôs beauty of never giving up. 

From the makers of iconic songs like Qismat , Maan Bhariya , Pachtaoge  and Coka , one of bollywood most celebrated Artist Akshay Kumar  Featuring Nupur sanon , bring to you, their first ever debut Music video , in the voice of Bpraak . The video , shot is done by the concept king Arvindr Khaira  and penned down by one and only lyrical machine JAANI . Filhaal, a song that depicts the story of that true love which is pious, selfless yet incomplete. 

Desi Melodies proudly presents FILHALL  In association with cape of Good films & Azeem Dayani

snippet.title: Esports World Cup 2025 Day 1 | Rd. of 16 | ft.Carlsen, Naka, Nihal, Arjun, Anish (Hindi Commentary)
snippet.description:
The E-sports world cup 2025 begins on 29th July and goes on until 1st of August 2025. It's a 16-player event with some of the biggest names in the world of chess! 

The commentary will be in Hinglish. Watch on Sony Liv without 7 minutes delay: https://www.sonyliv.com/live-sport/e-sports-world-cup-2025-1790006658/esports-chess-at-ewc-25-day-1-group-stage-29-jul-2025-1090485632?watch=true&utm_source=Share&utm_medium=social_share
Let's try and understand the format:

16 players are segregated in group of 4 players. So there are 4 groups in all. The time control is 10+0. 

These are the groups and matches:
Group A:
Nepo vs Esipenko
Artemiev vs Aronian

Group B: 
MVL vs Anish Giri
Nihal Sarin vs Arjun Erigaisi

Group C:
Nakamura vs Sindarov
Wei Yi vs Firouzja

Group D:
Carlsen vs Nodirbek
Duda vs Caruana

Best of 2 games followed by Armageddon. The two winners in each group will play each other to move to the Semi-finals, while the two losers will play each other in the losers bracket. On 29th of July we have the round of 16 and the quarter-finals taking place.

Video: ChessBase India
